#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; is a text editor by &kde; allowing you to edit one file at the time "
"per window."
msgstr ""
"El &kwrite; és un editor de text per al &kde; que permet editar un fitxer "
"alhora per finestra."

